[Student "S"]
{SOUTH has 11 points and five \Hs, so she responds 
2\D as a Jacoby Transfer.

When NORTH bids the required 2\H, SOUTH jumps to 3NT 
to show at least 11 points, but only a 5-card \H suit.

Since NORTH has only a doubleton \H she passes 3NT.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "3"]
